title: Fellowes Powershred® 60Cs 10-Sheet Cross-Cut Shredder
description:
The Powershred® 60Cs Cross-Cut Shredder features SafeSense® Technology that stops shredding when hands touch the paper opening. The 60Cs shredder can shreds up to 10 sheets per pass into 5/32"x 2" cross-cut particles (a Security Level P-3). It can shred for up to 6 minutes before a 30 minute cool down period is needed. The shredder comes with a 6 gallon waste bin. It includes a 1 year product warranty and 5 year cutter warranty.

Fellowes Powershred® 60Cs 10-Sheet Cross-Cut Shredder w/ SafeSense® Technology
* Equipped with Safe Sense Technology that stops shredding when hands touch the paper opening
* Shreds 10 sheets per pass
* Shreds for up to 6 minutes w/ 30 minute cool down period
* Features a 6 gallon bin
* 1 yr product warranty; 5 yr cutter warranty
